ns0:foreignObject.html:div: Carefully observe the educational illustration showing Elements of the weather. Use the details from the image to answer the following questions. Fill in the blanks with the correct words or numbers.

ns0:svg.ns0:text: 1. The illustration shows different elements of the _______________ (1).
2. The image depicts a thermometer measuring the _______________ (2).
3. If the temperature is 25 degrees Celsius and it increases by 5 degrees, the new temperature will be _______________ (3) degrees Celsius.
4. The amount of rain measured in the illustration is _______________ (4) mm.
5. If the wind speed is 15 km/h and it doubles, the new wind speed will be _______________ (5) km/h.
